<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (frḥt qlby ywm mạ qbltk ywm mạ qbltk kạn ywm ʿyd)2
 (kẖlṣtny ryḥt ḍmyry gẖyrt qlby bqlb jdyd)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̹nt ḥbyby ạ̹nt ḥyạty ạ̹nt nṣyby ạ̉ʿẓm nṣyb)2
 (ạ̉ḥbbtny yạ yswʿ wạ̉nạ kẖạṭy ḥbk ẓhr ly fy ạlṣlyb)2
 2- (smʿt ṣwtk bynạdyny fy ậyẗ mn ậyạt ạlạ̹njyl)2
 (wjdt fyhạ tʿzyạty wkạn ṣwtk wạḍḥ wjmyl)2
 3- (fy lḥẓẗ wạḥdẗ ạ̉tgẖyr ḥạly sẖʿrt ạ̹ny ạ̹nsạn jdyd)2
 (sʿạdẗ lm tkẖṭr ʿly̱ bạly frḥ lạ ynṭq bh wmjyd)2
 4- (ʿndk nʿm wḥyạẗ ạ̉bdyẗ ʿndk ynbwʿ yrwy ạlʿṭsẖạn)2
 (ạ̹rwyny mn nbʿk yạ fạdy lky ạ̉kwn dwmaⁿạ frḥạn)2</lyrics>
<title>frḥt qlby ywm</title>
